# vue-tab-complete-input

A tab completable <input> component for Vue.js

# Demo

Try tabbing these names: Dena, Cassidy, Darius, Jewel, Bradley, Emmet, Chet, Marilou, Gus, Triston, Rossie, Kattie, Karina, Zackary, Enrico, Pierce, Stuart, Kaylie, Willy, Zane

# Install

yarn add vue-tab-complete-input

# Include

<tab-complete-input v-model="text" :data-source="list" />

<script>
  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        list: [],
        text: ''
      }
    },
  }
</script>
